                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-oswald mb-2">23-28% of Students</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">Nationally, **nearly 1 in 4 students (23-28%)** were chronically absent in 2023-24, missing 10% or more of school days and creating significant learning gaps.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-card p-8 centered-section flex flex-col animate-fade-in card-2">
                    <div class="text-zt-orange text-5xl mb-4"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up-right-dots" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-oswald mb-2">A Path to Re-Engagement</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">A 2015 meta-analysis found after-school programs show **promise in reducing externalizing behaviors**, though effects on attendance were not significant.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-card p-8 centered-section flex flex-col animate-fade-in card-3">
